      <h2>Biography</h2>
      <p>Sascha Star (born October 5, 1977, in Rijeka, Croatia) is a Croatian actor, singer, television host, and writer who lives and works between Zagreb, Belgrade, London, and Los Angeles. His career spans over two decades, with a strong presence in both European and American entertainment industries.</p>
      <p>He studied at the American Academy of Dramatic Arts and began his career as a model for Emporio Armani. He later founded Sascha Star Studio and Sascha Star Sound, with his debut album <em>Casablanca</em> currently in production.</p>
      <p>His first book, <em>One Hundred Days in the Month</em>, is available for pre-order. The Croatian publisher remains confidential.</p>
